extendedInfo.description: Each day is a new pursuit as the environment develops around you.In this colorful world, Grandma, the dog and a couple of nasty crows are all out to get you! Take to the streets as a fat cat with stolen sausages. Test your reflexes as you zip across rooftops, tippy-toe over power lines and dash along ledges. Swipe to turn, slide and jump to avoid danger while earning coins, special bonuses and power-ups.  Challenge and beat your Facebook friendsâ high score and become the top cat!3 unique cats available, each with their own special abilities.
